::::'''Old Garmentmaker:''' Well hello, my esteemed guest... we meet again.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} This has to be a dream.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504118003-->
:::::'''Old Garmentmaker:''' In a way, you're right. I exist here thanks to your active imagination.
::::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you from the new world?
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504118005-->
:::::'''Old Garmentmaker:''' I don't believe so. My connection to you is more intimate than to the outside world.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504118006-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504118006-->
::::'''Old Garmentmaker:''' Aedes Elysiae is influenced by a unique power that molds me from your memories &mdash; magic, one might say.
::::'''Old Garmentmaker:''' In this form, I inherit the ability to sense weavers and the duty to collect nymphs. I'm sure you recall my former purpose.
::::'''Old Garmentmaker:''' Regardless, thank you for your continued assistance. If you find any nymphs, please lend a hand.
::;(Subsequent interactions)
